{"tid":566951,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[討論] 死亡台","createTime":"2018-02-20T11:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T05:39:55.000Z","uid":79353,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5e32d101268e1a82788c735a64aaed2af0381050","tid":566951,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"講下你地對死亡的任何想法/幻想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得死係一件好孤獨既事<br />\n死果陣好孤獨<br />\n如果真係有下世，人死左後會去另一個空間，咁我更加覺得，人死既時候好孤獨。"},{"pid":"a30a104dd1bb66739c3e4f46b83cf60ec44ef90e","tid":566951,"uid":7306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"乜都無"},{"pid":"ce535cbd788d0c10b50334521f091147c9c225d7","tid":566951,"uid":151926,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"冇哂意識<br />\n好似訓著左咁<br />\n不過唔會發夢"},{"pid":"4a1e4c793e5e633dd273eaadb5f09ef3477495fe","tid":566951,"uid":172589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"或者死左係件好事呢<br />\n咩都唔駛煩"},{"pid":"8d72dcc7e42a06116cb5f35894c518fe14c2c875","tid":566951,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"生存緊嘅時候係為左一個唔存在嘅目的：唔死"},{"pid":"b211c6f523a9891b88b0b8f56a01c92d3c3895c5","tid":566951,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"咁點解要浪費時間 或者能量 去生存"},{"pid":"ad00244415047b9207c2ff0b3783554e86adab1e","tid":566951,"uid":172613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"如果可以會揀唔投胎，睇住個世界點變"},{"pid":"55fb75f75d15718fce08ede57ec164e46129517c","tid":566951,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"不嬲孤獨開唔怕<br />\n<br />\n解脫 轉化 重生<br />\n但好多嘢未做"},{"pid":"7dababf2d915c93d97d0f1aa277b2e576c0b974c","tid":566951,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T21:32:56.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到其實自己唔會知自己已經死咗"},{"pid":"f6925a4f80e63a3f0d83362e1f0993e314276b21","tid":566951,"uid":136900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T21:34:48.000Z","msg":"今日先有親人離世<br />\n真係好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee57357b3289a56904bc8f08e6bdd6ad181fd7c4","tid":566951,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"以前我以為自己唔怕死亡依樣野<br />\n<br />\n但我好怕望住親人慢慢步向死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好想佢地可以生存耐啲, 但無能為力個種感覺好痛苦<br />\n<br />\n我好怕自己會早死, 因為我死咗, 我屋企人一定好傷心, 我又照顧唔到我屋企人<br />\n<br />\n所以我好希望我所有屋企人走曬先到我"},{"pid":"ee253e73346ea262de67ab545cfa71767441ef0f","tid":566951,"uid":140135,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"人死如燈滅 可能本身呢個世界就係一場夢 <br />\n死左之後全部野都會消失"},{"pid":"1dff27e26d620fbf7d551473ca4519e5e11d93f9","tid":566951,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e32d101268e1a82788c735a64aaed2af0381050","tid":566951,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"講下你地對死亡的任何想法/幻想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得死係一件好孤獨既事<br />\n死果陣好孤獨<br />\n如果真係有下世，人死左後會去另一個空間，咁我更加覺得，人死既時候好孤獨。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T01:59:35.000Z","msg":"死後 == 生前"},{"pid":"d8ae77104d5191240ac8d63238ab7ae4e85b8531","tid":566951,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dff27e26d620fbf7d551473ca4519e5e11d93f9","tid":566951,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e32d101268e1a82788c735a64aaed2af0381050","tid":566951,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"講下你地對死亡的任何想法/幻想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得死係一件好孤獨既事<br />\n死果陣好孤獨<br />\n如果真係有下世，人死左後會去另一個空間，咁我更加覺得，人死既時候好孤獨。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T01:59:35.000Z","msg":"死後 == 生前"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"死左之後的你 == 你在母體懷孕前的你<br />\n<br />\n例如你1979年懷孕，1980年出世，2065年死亡。<br />\n咁對你黎講，2066年的你，就等於1978年的你。<br />\n<br />\n當然，呢個係唯物論的睇法<br />\n<br />\n宗教睇法又好唔同，depends on你信的宗教。又些人通靈，又認為人靈魂不滅。<br />\n<br />\n另外，科技方面，有少數人會玩人體冷凍技術，大約花3萬美元，將自己冷凍，期待未來科技可以將佢解凍復活。"},{"pid":"97d1d91bfd502abeb6d20a069680763293a8a0e1","tid":566951,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"由你後代嘅眼去睇呢個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68a0f15822bcd2ded2bf2f1644353e4a4008277","tid":566951,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"長眠發長夢一世唔醒"}]}